Text: EGM Weekly Staff Meeting Reminder Cc reminder that the EGM weekly staff meeting will take place on Monday June th from am in video conference room EB C The staff meetings will continue on a weekly basis on every Monday at the same time and location unless notified otherwise Please let me know if you are unable to attend Thank you Cathy Phillips X
